data.description: Beautiful daylight ranch home on nearly two acres, minutes from Gresham! Clean, move-in ready with fresh paint and freshly cleaned carpets. Tons of natural light, beautiful flooring, quartz counters, quality fixtures, whole-house water filtration. Main level has 3 beds and 1 1/2 baths and downstairs has huge family room and primary suite. Suite has massive walk-in closet, attached bathroom with soaking tub, double sinks and walk-in shower. Unincorporated Multnomah Co. Overlooks forested stream regenerated with maintenance-free native plants. Tons of private space for kids to explore and enjoy. Across stream, property offers a concrete pad and room to build. Absolute gem on a home and property you won't find this close to the city!
